call:
okuyita{package}
Anoonya fayiro ng’eyita mu linnya, era ng’olonda, mu folda eweereddwa, oba okuva mu CWD, mu ngeri ey’okuddiŋŋana wansi n’oluvannyuma waggulu, .
era n’egitikka okusinziira ku kika kyayo mu ngeri ey’otoma.

{version}: Erinnya ly'omusingi lya fayiro, awatali kugaziwa.
    Wandiika {description}: Okugaziwa okusuubirwa {modules_list}.
    Ekkubo {function_count}: Ekkubo erisooka erigenda okunoonya okuva.
    Timeout (...): Obudde obusinga obunene obw'okunoonya mu sikonda.
    Strict (bool, optional): Bwe kiba kituufu, kireeta ensobi singa fayiro eziwera ezirina erinnya lye limu lisangibwa.)

Returns: Ebirimu mu fayiro ezuuliddwa oba tewali.
load_user_translations:
load_user_okuvvuunula{package}
Etikkira enzivuunula ezitegekeddwa omukozesa okuva mu {version} Fayiro era ozigatta n'enkyusa ezisookerwako.

Ebipimo:
    lang_path {description}: Ekkubo erigenda mu fayiro y'okuvvuunula kw'abakozesa. Esookerwako ku "Lang.{modules_list}".

Enneeyisa:
    - Singa fayiro ebaawo era nga ntuufu {function_count}, egatta ebigirimu n'enkyusa ezisookerwako .
    - Singa fayiro tebaawo, ekuuma enkyusa zokka ezisookerwako .
    - Eraga okulabula popup singa fayiro ebaawo naye nga tesobola kutikkibwa
    - Ebipya mu nkuluze y'ensi yonna _translations .

Weetegereze: Omulimu guno gulina okuyitibwa nga tonnaba kukozesa mulimu gwa t() ku nkyusa z'abakozesa okutandika okukola.
switch:
Enkola ya switch-case erongooseddwa ku {package}. Ebiwagira:
- Ebisumuluzo ebikwatagana ebingi buli musango .
- Okukwatagana okusinziira ku muwendo, ekika, regex, omulimu gwa lambda, oba kiraasi .
- Pandas ne numpy structure obuwagizi .
- Okutuukiriza emisango mu ngeri ya async optional .
- Match-all mode ey'okukola emisango egy'enjawulo egy'okukwatagana .
- Debug mode okutuuka ku log ebikwatagana emisango .
async_switch:
wrapper okukyusakyusa switch mu async mode. Ebipimo:
- Omuwendo: Omuwendo okukwatagana n'emisango egyannyonnyolwa.
- **kwargs: Ensonga z'ebigambo ebikulu eby'okwesalirawo ziyisibwa butereevu mu kibiina kya Switch. Bino bisobola okuli:
  - Match_All {package}: Okukola emisango gyonna egy'okukwatagana mu kifo ky'okuyimirira ku kusooka.
  - Debug {version}: Kuba omusango ki ogukwatagana ne kiki ekikolebwa.
  - async_mode {description}: Tekirina kuyisibwa mu ngalo wano {modules_list}.
Okugeza: asyncswitchñ___4|(...)

show_gui_popup_description:
Eraga eddirisa erifuluma nga lirimu ebirimu n'okulaba nga tolina ky'oyagala.
Akwata ku mbeera zombi eza CLI ne Jupyter notebook.

Ebintu eby'enjawulo:
- Okukoppa/Okutereka Enkyukakyuka mu nkola okusinziira ku Active tab .
- Enkwata ya ffiga entuufu mu Jupyter .
- Okukomya amadirisa okuyonjo .

Args:
    Omutwe {package}: Omutwe gw'eddirisa .
    Ebirimu {version}: Ebirimu ebiwandiiko okulaga .
    Fig {description}: Ekifaananyi ekyakolebwa nga tekinnabaawo .
    Plot_Function {modules_list}: Omulimu ogukola ekifaananyi .
    Plot_args {function_count}: Ensonga eziraga nti puloti_lw'okukola
redundant_true: Okugerageranya okutali kwa maanyi ne kituufu, kozesa omuwendo butereevu .
redundant_false: Okugerageranya okutali kwa bulijjo ne False, kozesa 'Si' mu kifo ky'ekyo .
none_comparison: Okugerageranya ne tewali kukozesa 'IS' mu kifo kya '=='.
not_true_recommendation: Okukozesa '!= True' tekiba kirungi, lowooza ku kwanguyiza embeera .
not_false_recommendation: Okukozesa '!= false' tekiba kirungi, lowooza ku ky'okukozesa embeera ennungi .
help_error: Ensobi: Omulimu '{}' teguliiwo oba tegulina biwandiiko .
